How to build the program:
use "make client" to build the client
use "make server" to build the server
use "make clean" to clean the executable client and server

How to run the program:

on server side: bash ./server.sh <req_code>
on client side: bash ./client.sh <server address> <n_port> <req_code> <msg>

Which machine I use to build and test:
ubuntu1804-008

Version of compiler:
gcc 7.4.0

Version of make:
GNU Make 4.1
